One of the guild invited his friend in on the camp.<br>
After 10hr camp most of the guild had to log. I was there along with this nerco. She was there before I joined group, and the loot rule was to roll on the ring. Well the AC popped and she jump right on his corpse and looted the ring. I was ever furious at her. She tells me I was here so I am 1st serve. I have have sent her a tell that she could of never solo the AC and if it wasn't for guild member you would not be here now! I have reported her to her guild leader, apprently GM was no help again.And the guild member who invited her logged back on and found out what happen then camp before I could give him a piece of my mind.<br>
Well as of today I will no longer do AC now that I have been KS 2 times, and ninja looted. AC sucks. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyalinae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yalinae</A> at: 4/9/01 8:47:03 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uqman007.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Qman007</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#333333>(8/13/02 10:03:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=85.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: *sigh* ancient cyclop ring ninja</span><hr size=1> Ah I was about to slap down a post here about the ac but I thought I should look first, maybe there was another one already here, and here it is.....<br>
<br>
   I think this is one of the worst examples of camps that Verant has ever put together, hrs upon hrs of camping for an item only to have another person come and take it right our from underneath the camper. This item used to drop from najena, why was it changed? And why is it put on a &quot;rare&quot; spawn in a commonly trafficed zone? Yea I know about the other 2 spawns, the one in the karana's being the most rare. Would it be so terrible to put this item on a static spawn that required a solid 6 person group of 50's to get together to get a guildmate jboots? Or is it that Verant wants these ppl to waste hrs upon hrs camping spawns with no reason. Heck with run3 these boots are made almost useless. <p><a href="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.gaijindesign.com/lawriemalen/jedi/yoda.jpg" width="285" height="123" border="0"><br>:: how jedi are you? ::</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/udevictionmt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DevictionMT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 199<br> <font color=#333333>(8/14/02 4:09:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=85.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: *sigh* ancient cyclop ring ninja</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> Heck with run3 these boots are made almost useless.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
